On Thursday, March 03, 2005, at 10:08PM, Tom Tarka <tommy(-at-)slackers.net> wrote:

> I assume this is the edge of the valve 
>seat.  I'm presuming that this is a sign of impending doom?
>
>Or is this normal?

If the valve seats are oversized I think it's normal. If not, then there is probably a problem. You can do a quick test by filling up the ports with mineral spirits and see if any fluid leaks thru to the combustion side.

